Package com.groq.sdk.models.batches

Class Batch

java.lang.Object
com.groq.sdk.models.batches.Batch
public class Batch extends Object
Represents a batch processing job with its current status and metadata. Tracks the progress and results of batch operations.

Batch jobs are used for processing large volumes of requests asynchronously. They can handle thousands of API requests in a single batch operation.
